      "amount": "1/4 cup",
      "notes": "chopped"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in the donabe over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they are tender.",
    "Add the sliced galangal and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the coconut milk and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Season the stew with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
